    <item>
      <title>匈牙利大选前，奥尔班将支出目标锁定农村养老金领取者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/orban-targets-rural-pensioners-with-spending-before-hungary-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 希望在关键选举之前提振日益低迷的支持率，因此将向农村地区的养老金领取者发放补助金，帮助他们翻修房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/orban-targets-rural-pensioners-with-spending-before-hungary-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:32:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟主要国家加大力度提高银行竞争力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/top-eu-nations-intensify-push-to-make-banks-more-competitive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国、法国和意大利正在加大游说力度，要求紧急审查欧洲银行业的弱点，包括提供帮助银行与美国大型竞争对手竞争的方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/top-eu-nations-intensify-push-to-make-banks-more-competitive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普接管加沙的想法加剧中东分裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普接管人口稀少的加沙的想法在以色列受到广泛欢迎，官员们称赞这一意外提议是加强与哈马斯战争后安全的一种手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国邮政局撤销暂停向中国发货的决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国邮政局周三表示，正在接受来自中国和香港邮政的“所有国际入境邮件和包裹”。几个小时前，该机构宣布暂停部分货物的收发。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/us-postal-service-says-it-s-accepting-china-hong-kong-packages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦大亨正在商谈向国家支付 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/kazakh-tycoon-in-talks-on-making-1-billion-payout-to-the-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为哈萨克斯坦政府对该国第一任总统任期内积累的财富进行调查的一部分，哈萨克斯坦最富有的人之一正在商谈向国家支付约 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/kazakh-tycoon-in-talks-on-making-1-billion-payout-to-the-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国贸易威胁 加拿大考虑增加向中国运输石油的方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-24-billion-trans-mountain-pipeline-accelerates-push-to-look-beyond-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自五月加拿大跨山输油管道扩建工程完工以来，几乎每天都有一艘满载油砂原油的油轮通过该管道穿过温哥华的狮门大桥，运往太平洋周围的炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/canada-s-24-billion-trans-mountain-pipeline-accelerates-push-to-look-beyond-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称希望新核协议让伊朗“繁荣”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-says-he-wants-new-nuclear-deal-allowing-iran-to-prosper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周三表示，他愿意立即开始与伊朗达成新的核协议，使伊朗能够“和平发展和繁荣”，这似乎软化了他对伊朗伊斯兰共和国的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-says-he-wants-new-nuclear-deal-allowing-iran-to-prosper</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团首席执行官称马里矿业发展令人深感担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/anglo-ceo-says-mali-mining-developments-cause-for-grave-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团首席执行官邓肯·万布拉德表示，马里政府对采掘业的改革可能会阻止企业在该国投资，该国拥有世界第二大金矿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/anglo-ceo-says-mali-mining-developments-cause-for-grave-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历史性减税措施出台后莫迪面临重大选举考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度首都的选民于周三参加了投票，这对总理纳伦德拉·莫迪来说是一次至关重要的考验，十多年来，他的政党一直未能从一个规模虽小但实力强大的竞争对手手中夺取德里的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/modi-faces-first-major-electoral-test-after-historic-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚电视内阁会议陷入混乱和泪水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/televised-colombian-cabinet-meeting-descends-into-rancor-tears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗 (Gustavo Petro) 的部长们互相指责，表达个人不满，此次内阁会议首次电视直播，但会议却陷入激烈争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/televised-colombian-cabinet-meeting-descends-into-rancor-tears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
